    </node>
    <node id="RT-DETR">
      <data key="entity_id">RT-DETR</data>
      <data key="entity_type">artifact</data>
      <data key="description">RT-DETR is a real-time end-to-end object detection model proposed in the paper, designed to outperform YOLOs in both speed and accuracy.&lt;SEP&gt;RT-DETR is a real-time end-to-end object detector proposed in the text, designed to improve inference speed and accuracy.&lt;SEP&gt;RT-DETR is an object detection model represented by red circles in the scatter plot, labeled as "Ours".&lt;SEP&gt;RT-DETR is a real-time end-to-end object detection model proposed in the paper, designed to improve upon DETRs.</data>
      <data key="source_id">chunk-304395e843a4ed6d59b25d1e18f87724&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-901133dd8268b83119819931e3df4d8a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6b2736f01bc36e3d1371f9309a3ef7a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a5620b1fca659e335baa5d632dacaf7a</data>
