      <data key="entity_id">T4 GPU</data>
      <data key="entity_type">naturalobject</data>
      <data key="description">T4 GPU is a graphics processing unit used for testing model performance.&lt;SEP&gt;T4 GPU is a type of graphics processing unit used for running and benchmarking object detection models.&lt;SEP&gt;T4 GPU is the hardware platform on which RT-DETR's performance is measured.&lt;SEP&gt;T4 GPU is a graphics processing unit used for testing and optimizing object detection algorithms.</data>
