      <data key="entity_type">concept</data>
      <data key="description">Real-Time DEtection TRansformer is the full name of RT-DETR, representing a novel approach to real-time object detection.&lt;SEP&gt;Real-Time DEtection TRansformer (RT-DETR) is a real-time end-to-end object detection model proposed in the paper, designed to outperform YOLOs in both speed and accuracy.&lt;SEP&gt;Real-Time DEtection TRansformer is the full name of RT-DETR, an efficient object detection model.</data>
