      <data key="entity_type">concept</data>
      <data key="description">Confidence threshold is a parameter used in NMS to filter out prediction boxes with scores below a specified value.&lt;SEP&gt;Confidence Threshold is a parameter used in NMS to filter output boxes.&lt;SEP&gt;Confidence Threshold is a parameter used in object detection algorithms that determines the minimum confidence level for detecting objects.</data>
